title: University of Wales Trinity Saint David Student designs logo for Canolfan S4C Yr Egin 23.10.2015 ...
text: ( Source : Swansea Metropolitan University ) 23.10. 2015 A student who's embarking on his final year of study at the University of Wales Trinity Saint David has designed the logo for Canolfan S4C Yr Egin - a centre for the creative industries
